KCCAns: Hand weeding should be done before fertlizer applicationat least 2-3 times at 20 days interval starting 20 days after planting. Wherever weed problem is acute, herbicides such as Butachlor (1.5 kg a.i/ha), Anilophos (0.6 kg a.i/ha), Pentachlor (0.4 kg a.i/ha) or any one of them in combination with 2,4-D (0.4 kg a.i/ha) should be applied, followed by need based hand weeding 20 days later.
